an’s Next Movie Titled ‘Split,’ Set for January, 2017 Release|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/m-night-shyamalan-split-january-1201627822/|accessdate=2015-12-08|work=variety.com|date=2015-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210222938/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/m-night-shyamalan-split-january-1201627822/|archive-date=2015-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

電影正式於2015年11月11日在[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]的[[費城|費城]]開拍<ref>{{cite news|title=M. Night Shyamalan Movie To Block Bike Lanes Next Week|url=http://bicyclecoalition.org/m-night-shyamalan-movie-to-block-bike-lanes-next-week/#sthash.o9f7addD.J77ozQx1.dpbs|accessdate=2015-12-08|work=bicyclecoalition.org|date=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210215656/http://bicyclecoalition.org/m-night-shyamalan-movie-to-block-bike-lanes-next-week/#sthash.o9f7addD.J77ozQx1.dpbs|archive-date=2015-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=M. Night Shyamalan’s ‘Split’, starring James McAvoy, filming locations in Philadelphia|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/11/12/m-night-shyamalans-split-starring-james-mcavoy-filming-locations-in-philadelphia/|accessdate=2015-12-08|work=onlocationvacations.com|date=2015-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120053657/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/11/12/m-night-shyamalans-split-starring-james-mcavoy-filming-locations-in-philadelphia/|archive-date=2015-11-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。沙馬蘭在看過《[[靈病|靈病]]》（2014年）後對該片的攝影風格大為讚賞，便請來了《靈病》的攝影師麥克·吉歐拉基斯；而美術設計師瑪拉·里波-施魯普則是沙馬蘭看完電視劇《[[無間警探|無間警探]]》後請來的<ref name="DVD (The Making of Split)"/>。儘管未宣布何時[[殺青|殺青]]，但於2016年6月7日，劇組重拍了部分片段<ref>[https://www.instagram.com/p/BGX2lwbCkRw/ Betty Buckley's instagram]</ref>。在後製過程中，[[斯特林·K·布朗|斯特林·K·布朗]]在當中所飾演的佛萊徹醫生的鄰居鏡頭已被刪除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/m-night-shyamalan-split-movie-interview/#synopsis-trailer|title=M. Night Shyamalan on His 3-Hour Cut of ‘Split’ and Why Sterling K. Brown’s Role Was Cut|website=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|first=Steve|last='Frosty Weintraub'|date=2017-01-17|accessdate=2017-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118053855/http://collider.com/m-night-shyamalan-split-movie-interview/#synopsis-trailer|archive-date=2017-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 主題 ==

演員{{le|貝蒂·芭克利|Betty Buckley}}稱該片處理燈光及拍攝的方式-{「}-非常優美且充滿藝術氣息-{」}-，就像是-{「}-一部法國片-{」}-<ref name="DVD (The Making of Split)"/>。製片人馬克·比安斯托克表示，-{「}-該片用一種微妙的方式呈現其風格，很自然，但是神秘又血腥-{」}-<ref name="DVD (The Making of Split)"/>。

==發行==
電影最初定於2017年1月27日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=Blumhouse Dates Two On Universal’s 2017 Schedule|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/blumhouse-untitled-films-2017-1201436717/|accessdate=2015-12-08|work=deadline.com|date=2015-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210182554/http://deadline.com/2015/06/blumhouse-untitled-films-2017-1201436717/|archive-date=2015-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後來改至2017年1月20日<ref name="ReleaseDate"/>。電影最先於2016年9月26日在[[奇幻電影節|奇幻電影節]]上首映。

===評價===
《分裂》整體獲得的評價以正面居多。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據278條評論，持有77%的新鮮度，平均得分6.4／10；該網站共識：「《分裂》以詹姆斯·麥艾維於多種角色上的戲劇性演技作擔當-並察覺編劇兼導演奈·沙馬蘭響亮地回歸到《驚心動魄》的模式」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/split_2017 |title=Split (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011055759/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/split_2017 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分62，代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/split|title=Split reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160930032455/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/split|archive-date=2016-09-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的反應在A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |access-date=2019-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210223808/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |archive-date=2019-12-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[衛報|衛報]]》的{{le|喬丹·霍夫曼|Jordan Hoffman}}給了4星（滿分5星），他評論：「希區考克式地巧妙結合了恐怖和治療過程」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/sep/27/split-review-james-mcavoy-m-night-shyamalan-fantastic-fest-austin |title=Split review – James McAvoy is 23 shades of creepy in M Night Shyamalan chiller - Film - The Guardian |accessdate=2016-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160930145114/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/sep/27/split-review-james-mcavoy-m-night-shyamalan-fantastic-fest-austin |archive-date=2016-09-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
北美方面，《分裂》與同期上映的《[[限制級戰警：重返極限|限制級戰警：重返極限]]》和《[[速食遊戲|速食遊戲]]》共同競爭，估計於首週末能從三千零三十八間戲院中獲得2000萬至2500萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-founder-box-office-preview-1201888052/ |title=‘Split’ And ‘xXx’ Merge Into Market While ‘The Founder’ May Get Lost In Heavy Traffic – Box Office Preview |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |access-date=2017-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803141311/http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-founder-box-office-preview-1201888052/ |archive-date=2017-08-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美國週四晚間，電影獲得200萬美元的票房，這表現比2015年的《[[探訪_(電影)|探訪]]》的100萬美元更好<ref name="Thursday">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4260&p=.htm |title='Split' Hauls in $2 Million from Thursday Previews, 'xXx 3' Delivers $1.2M |work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=2017-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122121152/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4260&p=.htm |archive-date=2017-01-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；為此分析師再估計首週末票房有望獲得3000萬至3700萬美元<ref>{{cite web|last1=Rose|first1=Steve|title=‘Split’ Soars To Mid-$30M After Solid $2M Start; ‘xXx,’ $1.2M, ‘Founder,’ $105K In Previews As ‘Hidden Figures’ Stays Strong|url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-found}}</ref>。美國首映週末票房收入為4020萬美元，位居當週票房冠軍，並在麥艾維主演的非《X戰警》系列電影中最高的首映成績<ref name="opening">{{cite web|title=Uni/Blumhouse’s ‘Split’ Is A Hit With High $39M To $40M+; ‘Xander Cage’ Falls Down|url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-founder-late-night-thursday-previews-box-office-1201889940/|access-date=2017-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803140008/http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-founder-late-night-thursday-previews-box-office-1201889940/|archive-date=2017-08-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後，《分裂》在美國連續蟬聯了三週的票房冠軍。

台灣方面，首週三天票房為新台幣4380萬元<ref>{{cite web |title=【分裂】再傳票房捷報！ |url=https://www.facebook.com/UniversalTaiwan/posts/10154372540001947/ |website=[[Facebook|Facebook]] |publisher=環球影片粉絲專頁 |date=2017-02-06 |access-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214202459/https://www.facebook.com/UniversalTaiwan/posts/10154372540001947 |archive-date=2019-02-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；次週票房累計至新台幣1億元<ref>{{cite web |title=【分裂】再傳票房捷報，全台票房破億！ |url=https://www.facebook.com/UniversalTaiwan/posts/10154390284596947/ |website=[[Facebook|Facebook]] |publisher=環球影片粉絲專頁 |date=2017-02-13 |access-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214202459/https://www.facebook.com/UniversalTaiwan/posts/10154390284596947 |archive-date=2019-02-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；最終全台票房為新台幣1.63億元<ref>{{cite web |title=全國電影票房截至2017年六月前資訊 |url=https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/全國電影票房截至2017年六月前資訊%20v2.pdf |website=[[國家電影中心|國家電影中心]] |date=2017-07-05 |access-date=2019-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180720140207/https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B32017%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%20v2.pdf |archive-date=2018-07-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

